      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>KURTZ-Ruth. On August 29, 2000. Beloved wife of the late Michael Kurtz. Dear mother of Dr. Robert S. Kurtz and Daniel Kurtz. Cherished grandmother of Holly, Elizabeth, Amy, Ben, Peter and Michael. Mother-in-law of Ketly and Elizabeth. We all share her cherished ideals. Graveside service Thursday, August 31st, 1:45PM at New Montefiore Cemetery, Farmingdale, N.Y.</p>
